text:
I don't think tujhse dosti na hoti toh meri college life same hoti. You have been one of the most important parts of my college life. Woh Anatargni mein chup kr sutte maarna and bahane banana (jis din abdul mile the xD), woh jaipur trip , surat trip and obviously goa. Antaragni mein saath mein rona, gaali khana - tu hamesha saath tha. Hopefully aage bhi rhega. Dance ka toh kya hi bolun meri college life mein tere se better dancer nhi dekha maine. You can do everything you put you mind to. 

Agli trip jald hi maarenge gandhi ke salary aane de xD.
author: Pragyan  Pandey

text:
"Pandey Yaar, hum bhut same same se hain"
Tere saath woh jo night-outs maare the abhi tak yaad hain. Apan ekdum bhut zyada nhi milte the but we were always there for each other. You are that one person - jisse mein relationships se leke placement tak ki baatein kr skta hun. Tere pe woh punjabi jokes maarna aur tera har cheez explain krte rhna - "bc punjabi and sardar alag alag hain". Tere saath bitching krna is too much fun. Milte hain Bangalore mein and let's start talking more and wing wale video call ya kuch ho toh aa jana bc.
author: Pragyan  Pandey

text: Pakirao bc surname ki spelling change kr pehle Paikrao kitna ajeeb hai. Bhut hi sweet banda hai tu, woh antaragni mein dance woh Galaxy mein jab OAT ja rhe toh hall 3 ke peeche xD, bakchodiyan khub ki hain apan. And hn woh Galaxy battle mein jo gaand phadi thi tune shayd hi main bhul skta. Dance ke alawa apan kam mile until these last 2 months and tu hamesha bhand mila mujhe xD. Dance krna chalu krde dobara and jald hi milte hain (agli baar trip plan ho aajana bsdk).
author: Pragyan  Pandey

text:
Bc Rawat Maine Search mein Rawat daala dikha nhi rha tha tera naam Akash daalna pada xD. Pehle toh as usual - "itna kadak kaise naachta hai bc, thoda body dheela toh chhoda kr". Tere baare mein pehli baar first year mein kisi se suna tha ki dance bhi kiya aur acads bhi sambhala. Tune kahi na mera dance club join krne ka dar nikal diya tha iss baat and that has been one of the best decisions of my college life. Bhut bakchodiyan ki hain apan and hn ek party lunga main tere se uss Flashmob ki xD. Hamesha motivated rhta hai aur priorities sort krke rkhta hai. Tereko kabhi randi rona krte hue nhi dekha jo bhi hai tu sambhal leta hai chahe acads chahe dance, bhut hi sincere hai tu.  Mast si placement lgwate hain phr apne laundon ke milke paise udate hain,

PS: Bhojpuri sikhate rhna xD
author: Pragyan  Pandey

text:
Chandu bhai - woh first year ki PE se last year ki infinite bakchodiyon tak. Kaafi time saath mein guzara hai apan ne. Woh Triund ka top ghodon ke beech bc. Tere se lko ki wajah se bhut apna apna si vibes aati hain. Jitna bhi bahar se bakchodi krta hai but andar se you are  a very caring soul. Gym jaana dobara start krte hain campus pahuch ke. 
Placement lgwa ke bali nikalte hain bitch. Milte hain( lko mein hi xD).
author: Pragyan  Pandey

text:
Dewansh bro, 
First of all tera meme knowledge next level hai xD. Pehla din tha college ka main aaya tha tere se baat krne and tune kaafi der tak baat ki thi and it made me feel ki bhut achcha aadmi hai tu. Woh ESC101 ka paper tha apan ne meme war start kr di thi woh kabhi nhi bhul skta main. Jab bhi apan interact kiye aur meri gaand phati hoti thi you were always very supportive. Woh raat bhar daaru ke baad kapde dhona toh bhul hi nhi skta main xD (Kuch zyada hi productive ho gya ekdum se). 
Jald hi milte hain lko mein bro and mahool banate.
author: Pragyan  Pandey

text: Itna sab kuch saath kiya hai kya hi likhun bc. Itne kaand, bakchodi, gossips ,  ladaiyan  (latest - "Maggi ka spoon" bc ). Saare midsem, saare endsem, intern (ppo leke nikal liya tu nhi toh saath mein hi place hote lol).  Its been a fucking rollercoaster and apan ek doosre ke liye hamesha khade rhe. Trip pe woh cranberry juice bc . We even share same likes , dislikes - Valorant. Bhut saari achchi memories and hopefully aur hongi. See you in Bangalore R*n*d*.
author: Pragyan  Pandey

text:
“Next round kon kon piyega”
Bhai Idk kaise itni capacity hai teri but kisi din toh tereko pura bhand krunga. 
Promise.

Tere ghar itni trips maar li hain ki now it feels like apna hi ghar hai xD. You are one of the most sincere guys I’ve ever met. Antaragni krna, acads mein chaapna aur hame (Mujhe and Aakarsh) ko roz practice ke liye uthana bhi. Teri sincerity kabhi bhi irritate bhi kr deti hai lekin seh lenge thoda. Apan ko bas tere ladkiyon ke taste pe kaam krna hai thoda xD. Baaki I’m still jealous of your smile. 

“Apan toh milte hi rhenge”
author: Pragyan  Pandey

text:
Jab bhi tujhe yaad krta hun - teri tikhi galiyan aa jati hain dimag mein xD. I don't remember kab apan itne achche dost ban gye. Woh bhatia ke saath lambi walk wali raat abhi bhi yaad hai. Tere jokes mein hamesha do teen layers hoti hain and I'm always like ki bc itna kaise sochta hai yeh. Woh gandhi ke room wali party ki raat abhi bhi yaad jab tune gale laga ke rakha tha mujhe kaafi der tak. Tu jitna andar se pyara hai dikhata nhi but deep down bhut pyaara insaan hai tu. From "mereko kaun psnd krega" to "Surat chalte hain" - kaafi bada ho gya hai bc.
Jaldi se PhD ke liye desh chhod main peeche peeche aata hun xD.

PS: Ambedkar Jayanti nhi bhul paaunga main.
author: Pragyan  Pandey

text:
Harshit bro,

Kaisa sa hai tu mereko hazam nhi hota itne achche bande hain bhi kya duniya main. Hamesha trips ke liye ready, hamesha help krne ke liye bhai kuch toh nakhre kiya kr. First year ki teri grand party yaad hai mujhe, you were like - "hn delhi mein toh itni ki hi deta tha main". Itna down to earth hai tu ki kya bolun. Dil ekdum bachche jaisa hai tera - hamesha khelne ke liye ready lol. Trip mast thi and hopefully aage wali trips aur khatarnaak hongi and hosh mein na rhun main toh sambhal lena. Thank You for always answering my placement queries and hn woh video mere pass abhi bhi hai jisme teri gaand maari thi. Woh first year mein Philosophy saath mein padhna aur MTH bhi. Achche din the woh. 
Jaldi hi milta hun (Delhi toh paas mein hai bc aata jaata rhunga xD).
author: Pragyan  Pandey

text:
"Sajal bsdk"
abhi bhi yaad tere mere room se chilana start kr dena sajal se room khulwane ke liye. First year mein kitna seedha tha bc, tere saare decisions mein thoda thoda role the mera - I feel good the way those turned out. The concept of bhai is truely meant for friends like you. Bhut bakchodiyan ki hain apan ne saath mein kitna hi likh paaunga main. You are a very pure soul. Aur bc job change krke bangalore chala ja jaldi :P. 
Milte hain trip pe!!
author: Pragyan  Pandey

text:
Madhur bhai,
1st year mein padhne mein alas krne se leke bina placement mein baithe job lgwana - bhut chaapu hai tu. Yeh toh bhut baar bol hi chuka hun main. Thanks for doing those DS assignments. Woh cranberry juice trip pe bc, woh acid trip mein red light. Saari parties and trips ki planning krna - hamesha hamare order lena. You are a great friend. Thanks for always being there for me. US jaane se pehle mil lena bc and December tak ruka toh hum noida aa jaaenge. Milte hain jald hi!!!
author: Pragyan  Pandey

text:
Mayur bsdk,
Apan mein ek alag si hi understanding and woh vibes mujhe sirf tere se milti. First year se - mini militia se chegg tak, bhut nashe kiye hain apan saath (chegg bhi nasha hai xD). Mereko woh parties yaad hain jab main kisi cheez ko hn bolta tha you were like - "Pandey ke liye pegg banao bc". You are one of those guys who are very close to my heart. Kabhi kabhi madarchodi krta hai but you usually make up for it. 
Placement lgwate hain and Bali nikalte hain.
author: Pragyan  Pandey

text:
Yo Mama!!!
I don't remember apan first time kab mile the, but I'm glad that we did. Bhut hi innocent soul hai tu and I love this about you. Hamesha Nayi cheezein try krwata rhta hume - "Arre kuch nhi hoga mama, tu try toh kr". And dheere dheere kab tu wing ka part ban gya pta bhi nhi chala. Kasol trip mein woh monkey cap pehen ke bus ke aage baith ke crush krna xD. The fact that you don't give a fuck to what people think about you is something maine bhut kam logon mein dekha hai. 
Milte hain campus mein and kasol dobara chalte hai xD.
author: Pragyan  Pandey

text:
Nikunj bsdk - kaisaaaa hai tu. 

Bhut body shame kiya hai tereko (I don't regret gym ja bsdk). Woh intern day 1 yaad hai mujhe jab tu interview deke aaya tha and tune mereko btaya ki tu pehla hai jisse bta rha ki lg gyi + you were like teri intern mein sbse pehle post main daalunga bc. Yeh choti choti cheezein dil ko chu gyi. From talking about JEE rank and srudying for DS together to daaru ke peg and chhat pe woh rona (Bc pata nhi tu roya tha ki hans rha tha xD) bhut achcha dost rha hai tu. Hamesha assignment jugadna aur woh Cheating L20 mein ES0203 mein toh nhi bhul paaunga main (7 log chaap rhe the bc). Tere chhote chhote randi rone ki "nhi be thoda sa hi paneer hai zyada mat le" bhut funny lgte the mujhe.
Aur abhi bhi hazam nhi hota tu Presi tha bc but seeing your name in the mails always made me proud. Woh second last raat itni cheezein batai thi tune mujhe (kaafi secrets I suppose - Bhatia types wale secrets nhi) and woh conversation adhuri hi reh gyi. 
Jaldi hi milenge and baat puri krenge (iss baar main secrets btaunga xD) and kaam krte krte busy mat ho jana.

PS: Achcha hua goa ke day 1 Jeep nhi li.
author: Pragyan  Pandey

text:
Sajal Sajal,
I still feel ki tu ek degree nhi do teen krke ja rha xD (meri included). Itna seedha tha first year mein bhai. Itne assignments, lectures. cheating bc, ab thesis mein tere bina thodi phategi meri lol. Woh kasol ki raat I still remember tereko khud ko control krta dekh bhut maza aaya. Almost Fakka khate khate bache and kya chutiya banaya prof ko. Also EE609 mein endsems tera endsem na hote hue bhi you studied for me and this is one of the many exams I can recall right now. You've been a friend who always has my back no matter what. Thanks for being so easy to talk to.

text: Still remember the day we met, first day of college - tu ekdum chikna good boy, Tereko woh 1st year mein gym ke liye uthana and tera bahana - "Bro saans nhi aa rhi" hamesha yaad rhega and udhar se apna gym bros banne tak ka safar. We have countless memories aur mostly mein hosh mein nhi honge apan especially with "THE GANG". You are one of the most chill and humble dudes I've ever met. You are one of those friends I'll cherish my whole life . Jald hi milte hain Nagpur mein xD.
author: Pragyan  Pandey

text:
Vishal bro,
First year mein kaisa ajeeb sa tu bc. But tab se you have evolved and for the better. Itna chaapu hai tu kya hi bolun - never got to say this on your face. Campus mein woh last ek mahina kaafi fun tha and we bonded a lot I guess. Hopefully We'll meet again at some point in life, But stay connected and hn wing group calls mein aate rhna. Geo-guesser apan khelte rhenge lol.
author: Pragyan  Pandey

text:
Yugesh bhai - Still remember the first day of college jab tu library nikal gya tha and honestly from the start you were different. First year se hi shayd hi kisi ne itna chaapa hai (atleast amongst the people i know) and aage bhi tu krta hi rhega. Thanks hamesha gyan dene ke liye jab bhi I was down. You are someone I can always look to for advice - chahe acads ho ya trades xD. We haven't talked much in these covid days but I remember that technical conversation with you and Madhur. You are someone to whom I look up to very often. Trip pe bhut bakchodiyan ki hai apan ne, woh police ka bus mein aana and tera bag khulwana jisme sirf gadgets the xD - uski bhi gaand phat gyi itna dekh ke toh.
Hopefully we'll meet sometime soon and Stay the amazing and helpful human  being you are.

PS: Biocon profit mein bech diya tha thanks to you :P.
